title: Mike Doughty - Circles Super Bon Bon (2013)
description:
Mike Doughty's latest album, which is a rehash of his Soul Coughing days. This is a rip from this [1] YouTube video, split and tagged.  I haven't seen this on any torrent sites so I figured I'd upload it.  Thanks to David Hausmaan for the original post.
